<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ men jìng jìng děng hòu 迦南513</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men jìng jìng děng hòu yé hé huá, wǒ men yī tóng guì xià qiú nǐ,
 yī shēng yī shì, yǒng bù lí kāi nǐ, ěr biān cháng cháng tīng dào nǐ de huà yǔ.</lyrics>
</song>